Title: Audrey Burnhep
Description:
I'm afraid I have nothing left to teach you, $n. However, your journey as a trainer is far from over!

Report to Audrey Burnhep in Stormwind. She has connections with many of Azeroth's finest trainers, and will help you grow further.
ObjectivesText: Report to Audrey Burnhep in Stormwind.
